  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 text-center">
    <p class="sl gp mb-4">Pinellas Park Roofing</p>
    <h1 class="font-display font-black tracking-tightest mb-5" style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5.5vw,4.5rem);line-height:.92;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:#1A1A1A">
      PINELLAS PARK ROOFING CONTRACTOR<br/><span class="gt">LICENSED & INSURED</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color:#555555;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.75">
      Pinellas Park property owners trust Happy Roof for reliable roof replacement, repair, and installation - residential and commercial. Strategically positioned between St. Petersburg and Clearwater along the Park Boulevard corridor, Pinellas Park is home to thousands of families and businesses that need a roofing contractor who shows up on time, does the job right, and stands behind the work. As a licensed and insured roofing contractor, we deliver that standard every day - backed by our 15-year workmanship warranty.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center mt-8">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-t">Get a Free Estimate <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
      <a href="tel:8135957663" class="btn-o call-tracking-number">Call (813) 595-7663</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- INFO STRIP -->
<div style="background:#FFFFFF;border-top:2px solid #E6A817;border-bottom:1px solid #E0E0E0;padding:.85rem 0">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-8 gap-y-2 font-display font-bold text-sm tracking-widest" style="color:#1A1A1A;text-transform:uppercase;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif">
      <span>Pinellas Park, FL</span>
      <span style="color:#E6A817">·</span>
      <span>CCC1337380</span>
      <span style="color:#E6A817">·</span>
      <span>HappyRoof.com</span>
      <span style="color:#E6A817">·</span>
      <span style="color:#3B9FD9">(813) 595-7663</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- WHY HAPPY ROOF IN PINELLAS PARK -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#FFFFFF">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-start">
      <div>
        <p class="sl gt mb-3">Why Happy Roof in Pinellas Park</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:1.5rem">WHY PINELLAS PARK PROPERTY OWNERS CHOOSE HAPPY ROOF</h2>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">
          Pinellas Park occupies a prime position in the center of Pinellas County, sitting directly between St. Petersburg to the south and Clearwater to the north. The Park Boulevard corridor is the city's commercial spine, lined with businesses, shopping centers, and restaurants, while the surrounding residential neighborhoods are home to a diverse mix of single-family homes, duplexes, and condominiums. The Gateway area on the city's eastern edge has seen significant commercial and industrial growth, adding warehouses, office buildings, and retail centers to the roofing landscape.
        </p>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">
          This blend of residential and commercial properties means Pinellas Park needs a roofing contractor capable of handling both a three-bedroom ranch home and a 20,000-square-foot commercial building with equal competence. Happy Roof serves both markets. Our residential division installs shingle, metal, and tile roofing systems on homes throughout the city. Our commercial capabilities include flat-roof systems, metal panel installation, and coating applications for the industrial and retail properties concentrated along Park Boulevard and in the Gateway district.
        </p>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">
          We hold Florida Roofing Contractor License #CCC1337380, carry full general liability and workers' compensation insurance, and pull all required permits with the City of Pinellas Park and Pinellas County. Whether you own a home near the city's residential core or manage a commercial property along Park Boulevard, we deliver consistent quality and back every project with a 15-year workmanship warranty in writing.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">15-Year Workmanship Warranty</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Every Pinellas Park roof we install comes with a written 15-year workmanship warranty - no exceptions, no fine print.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Residential & Commercial</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">We serve both residential homes and commercial properties throughout Pinellas Park, including the Park Boulevard corridor and Gateway area.</p></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICES IN PINELLAS PARK -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#F7F7F7">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p class="sl gt mb-3">Our Services</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em">ROOFING SERVICES WE OFFER IN PINELLAS PARK</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="scard p-8">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);margin-bottom:1rem">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Roof Replacement</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">
          Full tear-off and replacement for residential and commercial properties using Owens Corning Duration HDZ shingles, standing seam metal panels, concrete tile, or commercial flat-roof systems. Pinellas Park's proximity to both St. Pete and Clearwater means we can efficiently serve properties across the entire city. We handle decking inspection, underlayment, flashing, and every permit and county inspection. Most residential shingle roofs are completed in 1 to 3 days.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);margin-bottom:1rem">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Roof Repair</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">
          From missing shingles and cracked tile on residential homes to leaks and membrane damage on commercial flat roofs, we diagnose and repair roofing issues across Pinellas Park. The city's mix of older residential neighborhoods and active commercial zones means a wide range of repair needs - we handle them all. We respond quickly after storms and provide honest assessments without unnecessary upselling.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);margin-bottom:1rem">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 21H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h4"/><polyline points="16 17 21 12 16 7"/><line x1="21" y1="12" x2="9" y2="12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.75rem">Storm Damage & Insurance</h3>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">
          Pinellas Park is not immune to Florida's severe weather season. When tropical storms and hurricanes impact the area, we provide thorough damage assessments for both residential and commercial properties, document everything for your insurance claim, and coordinate directly with your adjuster. We work with all major insurance carriers in Florida and guide property owners through the entire claims process.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- OUR PROCESS -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#FFFFFF">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p class="sl gt mb-3">How It Works</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em">OUR 4-STEP PROCESS</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Free Inspection & Estimate</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">We inspect your roof from top to bottom - checking decking, underlayment, flashing, ventilation, and overall condition. You receive a detailed written estimate with material options, timelines, and transparent pricing. No pressure, no hidden fees.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Material Selection & Permits</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Choose your roofing material and color with our guidance. We pull all permits with the City of Pinellas Park or Pinellas County, order materials from the manufacturer, and schedule installation on a date that works for you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Professional Installation</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Our crew performs the full tear-off, inspects and repairs decking as needed, installs new underlayment and flashing, and lays your new roofing system to manufacturer specifications. We protect your property - landscaping, parking areas, and surrounding structures - throughout the process.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8 flex gap-5">
        <div class="step-num">4</div>
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:.5rem">Final Inspection & Warranty</h3>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">We schedule the county inspection to verify code compliance. Once passed, you receive your warranty documentation - including our 15-year workmanship warranty and manufacturer material warranty. We follow up at 30 days and 1 year.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SERVICE AREA -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#F7F7F7">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-10">
      <p class="sl gt mb-3">Pinellas Park Service Area</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:1rem">AREAS WE SERVE IN PINELLAS PARK</h2>
      <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto">Happy Roof provides residential and commercial roofing services throughout Pinellas Park and the surrounding communities. From Park Boulevard to the Gateway district, we have you covered.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-3 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Park Blvd Corridor</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Gateway Area</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">St. Petersburg</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Clearwater</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Largo</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Seminole</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Kenneth City</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Lealman</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Gandy Blvd</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Bardmoor</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#FFFFFF">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <p class="sl gt mb-3">Common Questions</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em">PINELLAS PARK ROOFING FAQ</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" onclick="this.setAttribute('aria-expanded',this.getAttribute('aria-expanded')==='true'?'false':'true');this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('open')">
        How much does a roof replacement cost in Pinellas Park?
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <div class="faq-answer-inner">Roof replacement costs in Pinellas Park typically range from $8,000 to $25,000+ for residential properties depending on size, pitch, material choice (shingles, metal, or tile), and whether structural repairs are needed. Commercial properties along Park Boulevard and in the Gateway area vary based on square footage and roof system type. Happy Roof provides free, detailed estimates with no hidden fees - call <a href="tel:8135957663" class="call-tracking-number" style="color:#3B9FD9;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">(813) 595-7663</a> for a personalized quote.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" onclick="this.setAttribute('aria-expanded',this.getAttribute('aria-expanded')==='true'?'false':'true');this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('open')">
        What roofing materials work best for Pinellas Park properties?
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <div class="faq-answer-inner">Pinellas Park's central location between St. Petersburg and Clearwater means properties face Florida's full weather spectrum - intense UV, heavy rain, and hurricane-force winds. Owens Corning Duration HDZ shingles rated for 130+ MPH winds are the most popular residential choice. Standing seam metal is ideal for both homes and commercial buildings, offering 40–60 year lifespans and energy savings. For the city's many flat-roof commercial and industrial properties, TPO and modified bitumen systems provide reliable, long-lasting protection.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" onclick="this.setAttribute('aria-expanded',this.getAttribute('aria-expanded')==='true'?'false':'true');this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('open')">
        Does Happy Roof handle permits for Pinellas Park roofing projects?
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <div class="faq-answer-inner">Yes. Happy Roof handles all permit applications with the City of Pinellas Park and Pinellas County building departments. We manage the entire permitting and inspection process - you never have to visit a government office or coordinate with an inspector yourself. All work is performed to current Florida Building Code standards.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" onclick="this.setAttribute('aria-expanded',this.getAttribute('aria-expanded')==='true'?'false':'true');this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('open')">
        How long does a roof replacement take in Pinellas Park?
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <div class="faq-answer-inner">Most Pinellas Park residential shingle roof replacements are completed in 1 to 3 days. Metal roofs typically take 3 to 5 days. Commercial projects vary based on building size and roof system but we provide detailed timelines during the estimate phase. Florida's summer afternoon storms can cause brief delays, but we plan around weather and keep you informed throughout the project.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" onclick="this.setAttribute('aria-expanded',this.getAttribute('aria-expanded')==='true'?'false':'true');this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('open')">
        Does Happy Roof handle commercial roofing in Pinellas Park?
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <div class="faq-answer-inner">Yes. Pinellas Park has a significant commercial and industrial presence, particularly along the Park Boulevard corridor and in the Gateway area. Happy Roof services commercial properties including flat-roof systems, metal roofing, and modified bitumen installations. We hold Florida Roofing Contractor License #CCC1337380 and carry full general liability and workers' compensation insurance for both residential and commercial projects. Certificates are available upon request.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
